Et quid in premissis duxeritis faciendum nos, infra xv dies post recepeionem Presencium inmediate sequentes, ubicumque in pro- gressu Visitacionis nostre prelibate fuerimus constituti, distincte et aperte certificetis, etc.—Dated at Ugborongh, 15 June.
